    def down_page_event(self):

        offset = self.offset

        datalist = self.datalist

        step = self.step

        if offset + step >= len(datalist):

            return

        self.menu_starts = time.time()

        self.offset += step



        # e.g. 23 + 10 = 33 --> 30

        self.index = (self.index + step) // step * step
